  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Medtronic is sponsoring a quality improvement study called Brady MX. It is hypothesized that
      lack of awareness of treatment and diagnostics pathways result in lower number of referrals
      to implanters of IPG.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
